â”œâ”€â”€ models/                # Versioned model artifacts
â”œâ”€â”€ mlruns/                # MLflow experiment tracking
â”œâ”€â”€ logs/                  # Structured application logs
â”œâ”€â”€ research/              # Exploratory notebooks
â”œâ”€â”€ src/                   # Production ML pipeline code
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ data_ingestion.py  # Data loading and validation
